The paper proposes a learning algorithm for artificial neural networks, which is related to the fields of neural networks (cs.NE), machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and natural language processing (cs.CL). The focus of the paper is on unsupervised learning, which is a common topic in the fields of neural networks and machine learning. The paper also mentions the use of feature detectors, which are commonly used in computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.NE and cs.LG, followed by cs.CV, cs.AI, and cs.CL.
